  "title": "速递｜“医学版 ChatGPT”OpenEvidence 两月估值翻倍至 120 亿美元，年化广告收入近 1.5 亿美元",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI4NTgxMDk1NA==&mid=2247512587&idx=3&sn=c9f33fa4f29fb0c4487de13a59fcf90c",
