  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-imgfileid=\"100001581\" data-ratio=\"0.6240740740740741\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=594ecc15&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fc1nmTeqRMZ1c9kib7nl2v8FqNowcvJPgSYxMN1jqqXDicdbaWN4Aic92MFt6NLrQ7YibdNc5778KYOEjBG4MPia8Riaw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D0\"></p>\n  <p style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;text-size-adjust:inherit;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-style:normal;margin-right:16px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.3);margin-left:16px;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;text-align:center;\" class=\"js_darkmode__0\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: left;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;font-size: 12px;\"><em><span style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;\" class=\"js_darkmode__1\"><span leaf=\"\">图片来源：OpenEvidence</span></span></em></span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\" class=\"js_darkmode__2\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">OpenEvidence</span></span></span><font face=\"宋体\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">运营着一款类似</span></span></span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">ChatGPT</span></span></span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">的产品，帮助医生从医学期刊和其他可信来源查找健康信息。</span></span></span></font></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\" class=\"js_darkmode__3\"><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">据一位交易知情人士透露，该公司正在进行</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">2.5</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">亿美元的股权融资，这笔融资完成后，这家成立三年的初创公司投后估值将达到</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">120</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">亿美元，较两个月前宣布融资时的上一轮私募估值翻了一番。</span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\" class=\"js_darkmode__4\"><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">如果交易完成</span></font><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">,</span><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">这家总部位于迈阿密的公司将成为八家估值超过</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">100</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">亿美元且年化收入超过</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">1</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">亿美元的</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">AI</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">应用开发商之一</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">,</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">根据</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">The Information</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">的生成式</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">AI</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">数据库。该公司通过向制药公司出售其聊天机器人上的广告位来赚钱</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">,</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">类似于谷歌在其搜索引擎上销售广告的方式。</span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\" class=\"js_darkmode__5\"><font face=\"宋体\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这项业务正在快速增长。<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">据交易知情人士称，</span></span></span></font><span style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">OpenEvidence</span></span></span><font face=\"宋体\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">目前的年化广告收入约为</span></span></span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">1.5</span></span></span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">亿美元，这意味着它目前每月产生超过</span></span></span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">1200</span></span></span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">万美元的收入。这比该公司</span></span></span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">8</span></span></span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">月份的广告收入增长了</span></span></span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">3</span></span></span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">倍。</span></span></span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\" class=\"js_darkmode__6\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">OpenEvidence</span><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">告诉潜在投资者，它目前只售出了十分之一的广告库存，这意味着如果售出其余部分，它可能产生超过</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">10</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">亿美元的年化收入。</span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\" class=\"js_darkmode__7\"><font face=\"宋体\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">该公司目前的毛利率高于</span></span></span></font><span style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">90%</span></span></span><font face=\"宋体\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">，在这方面超过了许多其他</span></span></span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">AI</span></span></span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">初创公司。</span>毛利率衡量的是公司在扣除服务其创收产品的直接成本（即收入成本）后从销售中获得的收益。知情人士表示，</span></span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">OpenEvidence</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">的收入成本包括运行服务器（包括为产品提供支持的</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">AI</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">模型）的费用，以及从医学期刊获得内容许可的费用。</span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\" class=\"js_darkmode__8\"><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">随着消费者越来越多地使用聊天机器人查找医疗信息，这轮融资应运而生。这推动聊天机器人制造商将资源投入到医疗保健相关功能上。例如，</span></font><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">OpenAI</span><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">在</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">8</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">月聘请了</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">Facebook</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">长期高管</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">Ashley Alexander</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">来开发与健康相关的产品。</span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\" class=\"js_darkmode__9\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">OpenEvidence</span></span></span><font face=\"宋体\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">针对的是医生而非消费者，医生使用其聊天机器人回答医学问题或分析同行评审的研究。</span>该公司表示，其聊天机器人比</span></span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">ChatGPT</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">等通用聊天机器人更准确，因为它是使用从医学期刊获得许可的信息开发的，例如《新英格兰医学杂志》。目前尚不清楚</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">OpenAI</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">是否也与医学期刊达成了类似的许可协议。</span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\" class=\"js_darkmode__10\"><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">交易知情人士表示，</span></font><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">OpenEvidence</span><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">还可以利用用户反馈来改进其搜索结果的排名。他们说，它还可以联系作为医生和细分领域专家的用户，帮助其训练</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">AI</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">更准确地回答细分问题。</span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\" class=\"js_darkmode__11\"><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">知情人士表示，该公司的产品使用开源</span></font><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">AI</span><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">模型搜索医学期刊并返回有用的信息和引用，以及为检索和搜索排名等任务训练的模型。它还使用来自谷歌、</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">OpenAI</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">和其他提供商的</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">AI</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">来总结其聊天机器人的回应。</span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;